-- Migration 034: Fill missing ballistic profile characteristics for demo readiness.
-- Scope: ballistic_profiles only. No custody, anomaly, ML, settings, or threshold data is changed.
-- This targets the older generic demo profile batch by test date so newer diversified seed data is left intact.

